data.description: Discover the epitome of comfort in this 3-bed, 1.5-bath Verdigris home, minutes from the schools. With a newer roof (Dec. 2017) durability, this residence seamlessly blends an open floor plan kitchen and living space. The kitchen delights with ample cabinets, a pantry, and a gas range. Newer wood veneer flooring adds warmth to the living area, and new carpet in 2 of the bedrooms (2023) installed as well. Step into a fully fenced backyard that backs onto a tranquil field, providing both privacy and scenic views. Ideal for gatherings or quiet family moments, this home is a perfect fusion of modern amenities and a prime location. Don't miss the chance to call this Verdigris gem your own – schedule a viewing today!
